-- Deutsche Bank Hires Anita Nemes as Global Head of Capital Introduction
-- Aaron Kirchfeld
-- 2010-06-29T14:58:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/deutsche-bank-hires-anita-nemes-as-global-head-of-capital-introduction.html

          
          
             Deutsche Bank AG hired Anita Nemes
as global head of capital introduction to help advise hedge
funds, according to a statement on its Web site.  
 Nemes, who will be based in London, will join the bank in
October from Bank of America Merrill Lynch, Deutsche Bank said.  
          
          


  


        